notes: Match delayed by exactly 2 hours due to a soaked ground. Reduced to a 35 over per side match, 7 overs maximum per bowler, fielding restrictions for 10 overs.
35th over: Reiffel to de Silva : 6 6 2 1 to Ranatunga: 2 1
SR Waugh hit 2 consecutive fours prior to being out
UDU Chandana took the wickets of Reiffel and Healy with consecutive deliveries. Fleming successfully played the next delivery, despite 5 fielders positioned around the bat on the off-side.
